Konotop 

On August 21th, Hitler ordered the Panzer Group 2 (Guderian) to advance southward to the Ukraine. Stalin reacted quickly and put the new 40th Army between the 21st and 13th Army near Podla at the Desna river.

On September 3rd, Guderian's troups built a beachhead on the Desna near Korop and Novgorod-Severskiv, and lateron approached the Seym river. After crossing the Seym, they could unite with the Panzer Group 1 (v. Kleist) ...

